snippet.textDisplay: I like this song but its lost its rustic folk punch.  HRH & Shruti hit the mark but why, why are we missing the dhol?!  Coke downplays the dhol.  Its off putting. This song however, is among the better compositions.  Hitesh retained the soul of this song and let HRH carry the song but had he used some folk instruments along it would have been sweet.  The same band in all the Coke compositions is starting to sound boring.  There should've been tumbi and dhol to add the punch.
snippet.textOriginal: I like this song but its lost its rustic folk punch.  HRH & Shruti hit the mark but why, why are we missing the dhol?!  Coke downplays the dhol.  Its off putting. This song however, is among the better compositions.  Hitesh retained the soul of this song and let HRH carry the song but had he used some folk instruments along it would have been sweet.  The same band in all the Coke compositions is starting to sound boring.  There should've been tumbi and dhol to add the punch.
